				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				I picked this spell up in the High Elf city, the first shop near the mage/wiz/enchanter guilds.  As was posted ealier, this is the safest way to explore the zone or maze without going there.  I normally cast it, target myself and go invis and sit(help with stamina loss) and just watch the screen.  Only problem is when something attacks you(as the caster) it is a bit of a pain finding the correct eye icon to cancel the spell.  Altho you can jump eye perspectives far away from your body, you cant use it to increase your attack spells (or at least I havent been able to).  Best way to explore places like MistMoore Castle is to wait for a train to run by and cast it on them when they return to the castle.  Great screen shots in places I will never see for a few levels.<BR>
